# Tailwind (build output only - source input.css IS committed)
# Note: tailwindcss.exe binary is NOT committed (downloaded at setup)
# But app.css IS committed so offline dev works without rebuild
# Uncomment if you want to rebuild dynamically:
# /static/css/app.css

