# Custom project-specific (MUST–GSL EMR)
# Keep these committed:
# - static/js/*.min.js (vendored HTMX, Alpine, idb, Chart.js)
# - static/css/app.css (Tailwind build output for offline dev)
# - requirements.txt (hash-pinned dependencies)
# - requirements.in (source of truth for deps)

# Ignore only:
# - .venv/ (above)
# - Local environment overrides (above)
# - Temporary seed/fixture files
/docs/temp/
/scripts/temp/
